{"type": "article", "id": 10665, "title": "Moky 隐形触摸板键盘", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-11T07:14:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235906lTX9BDQ5IWCmMs0c.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t如果你不想把你的平板电脑仅仅当作是个娱乐设备的话，你可能会需要一款键盘来搭配它。但如今市面上大多数的键盘都没能把触摸板的功能加进去。最近，来自韩国的设计师 Enyoung Cho 开发了一款名为「Moky」的隐形触摸板键盘，内置了红外光学触摸板，使用者只需将手指悬停在平板电脑上方，便可以控制屏幕上的光标，亦可以运用轻轻敲击键盘的方式来实现鼠标或是触摸板的点击功能。Moky 采用蓝牙 4.0 LE，可以连接智能手机与平板电脑等移动设备。目前，Moky 键盘正在 Indiegogo 网站上众筹，售价 69 美元（约合人民币 428 元），<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/moky-invisible-touchpad-keyboard#/story\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<iframe src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XMTI1OTYyMzY2NA==\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235903FinaoAchzXgdBkxt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523590472tZODukLSMRep8i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41442543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235904NDJIqcoz4WUCOHjl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235905SyOgmZdCJwsz06KR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052359055MhgxefHAuqw8TrQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04645477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n\n\n"}